94
00:11:29,357 --> 00:11:32,349
She need not necessarily be
a professional.

95
00:11:34,477 --> 00:11:37,230
I don't want to fail at
marriage at my age.

96
00:11:37,557 --> 00:11:40,947
I'd like to have enough time
to observe her.

97
00:11:41,877 --> 00:11:46,553
