-No, I can handle that.

101
00:12:00,997 --> 00:12:02,908
I have an idea.

102
00:12:05,197 --> 00:12:06,755
Have an audition.

103
00:12:10,837 --> 00:12:14,910
It'll be a romantic story.
Remember your documentary?

104
00:12:15,197 --> 00:12:19,509
Love triangle between dancer,
patron and a Down syndrome boy.

105
00:12:22,237 --> 00:12:24,467
Teamed up with a German TV station.

106
00:12:24,637 --> 00:12:27,674
I'll rearrange the story.
Any problems?

107
00:12:29,757 --> 00:12:34,751
I don't see any problems, but
we're going to audition?

108
00:12:35,077 --> 00:12:40,105
Trust me.
Have I ever disappointed you?

109
00:12:40,597 --> 00:12:41,996
Well no, but...

110
00:12:42,477 --> 00:12:45,275
The heroine is supposed to be
in her early 20's to 30.

111
