The conditions are that she be a well
trained person. No problems, huh?

112
00:12:49,757 --> 00:12:53,067
Wouldn't it be fraudulent?

113
00:12:53,597 --> 00:12:58,910
This audition is not only about finding
you a wife. It's part of making a movie.

114
00:12:59,277 --> 00:13:00,869
If we collect enough capital,
we can make the movie.

115
00:13:01,957 --> 00:13:04,187
The story isn't bad.

116
00:13:04,597 --> 00:13:06,235
Well...

117
00:13:08,517 --> 00:13:11,748
Am I supposed to marry
the main girl?

118
00:13:11,917 --> 00:13:16,229
No, a girl with that much talent
wouldn't marry you.

119
00:13:16,437 --> 00:13:18,826
They aren't the marrying type.

120
00:13:19,157 --> 00:13:24,629
Really good ones will always
fail the second interview.

121
00:13:24,997 --> 00:13:29,593
Really?
-Those are about 1% of all applicants.

122
00:13:30,837 --> 00:13:33,829
They are quite attractive.

123
00:13:34,557 --> 00:13:39,915
Smart, with a good upbringing.
Traditional and well trained.

124
00:13:40,477 --> 00:13:42,991
Wishing her to be your
son's wife?

125
00:13:43,597 --> 00:13:45,553
I don't get it.

126
00:13:45,717 --> 00:13:48,993
Why can't she get the main part?

127
00:13:49,237 --> 00:13:51,512
They are not unhappy.

128
00:13:52,157 --> 00:13:55,706
Happy people can't act well.

129
00:13:58,397 --> 00:14:03,346
And another thing. I have a plan to
work with FM, I'll combine this.

130
00:14:03,557 --> 00:14:07,345
Make another program
called "Tomorrow's heroine".

131
00:14:09,357 --> 00:14:13,430
Trust me.
I'm a pro at auditions.

132
00:14:16,997 --> 00:14:20,672
This is Yoshikawa. I'm in
room number 2. Coffee?

133
00:14:21,917 --> 00:14:25,546
Is coffee OK for you?
Bring two coffees please.

134
00:14:27,157 --> 00:14:30,467
I'm in a middle of a traffic
jam, I might be late...

135
00:14:33,837 --> 00:14:37,466
Please hand that tape to
Mr. Kaneda.

136
00:14:38,277 --> 00:14:40,154
Thanks.

137
00:14:48,517 --> 00:14:50,189
Tomorrow's heroine

138
00:14:50,397 --> 00:14:53,275
I'm just wondering
where you are?

139
00:14:53,597 --> 00:14:59,467
Wonderful things might happen. If you
encourage yourself a little bit more.

140
00:15:00,557 --> 00:15:06,427
Every star has their defining moment.
Hepburn and Julia Roberts.

141
00:15:06,717 --> 00:15:10,266
They led their own lives
prior to becoming heroines.

142
00:15:10,477 --> 00:15:15,471
