I'm sorry I ate your meal.
Terribly sorry.

197
00:22:09,717 --> 00:22:14,666
I will cook something for you.
-Don't worry about it. Take it easy.

198
00:22:16,717 --> 00:22:17,672
Gang.

199
00:22:25,157 --> 00:22:26,670
Good boy.

200
00:22:27,197 --> 00:22:29,427
Let's go for a walk.

201
00:22:29,957 --> 00:22:33,791
Shigehiko, make sure she gets
home alright. -Of course.

202
00:22:33,997 --> 00:22:35,794
OK boy, come on.

203
00:22:40,357 --> 00:22:43,190
Let's go Gang.

204
00:22:57,997 --> 00:22:59,350
Ready?

205
00:23:00,877 --> 00:23:04,187
Well... I feel like a criminal.

206
00:23:05,277 --> 00:23:06,756
I'm ready.

207
00:23:09,597 --> 00:23:10,791
Let's start.

208
00:23:11,957 --> 00:23:14,152
Pleased to meet you.

209
00:23:15,237 --> 00:23:16,431
Please sit.

210
00:23:22,517 --> 00:23:25,429
My name is Yu Tanaka.

211
00:23:25,797 --> 00:23:29,710
Please have a seat. Are you nervous?
-a little bit.

212
00:23:30,917 --> 00:23:33,351
Sorry, you are the first one.
-That's OK.

213
00:23:33,517 --> 00:23:35,985
We're going to tape you.
But don't worry. -OK.

214
00:23:36,317 --> 00:23:38,467
Do you mind if I ask what
your father's job is?

215
00:23:38,717 --> 00:23:42,107
Well... my father's...
job is...

216
00:23:42,557 --> 00:23:43,990
What can I say?

217
00:23:45,717 --> 00:23:46,991
Next one.

218
00:23:47,157 --> 00:23:52,151
I'm going to ask you frankly.
Why did you apply this part?

219
00:23:52,517 --> 00:23:54,906
Have you ever had sex with
someone you don't like?

220
00:23:55,237 --> 00:23:56,670
Are you interested in drugs?

221
00:23:56,877 --> 00:24:00,472
Can you act a little bit for us?

222
00:24:01,317 --> 00:24:03,672
Sure.
-Go ahead.

223
00:24:08,157 --> 00:24:09,670
What music do you like?

224
00:24:09,877 --> 00:24:12,914
Which actress do you like?
-I like Mituko Mori.

225
00:24:13,117 --> 00:24:13,867
Next.

226
00:24:18,837 --> 00:24:22,750
I used to love sports.
At school, I played...

227
00:24:23,157 --> 00:24:25,307
Did you ever want to work
for the sex industry?

228
00:24:25,757 --> 00:24:29,716
I have a friend who is
working in that area.

229
00:24:30,557 --> 00:24:31,546
Next.

230
00:24:41,717 --> 00:24:44,868
What are men to you?
Have you ever seen Tarkovsky movies?

231
00:24:45,117 --> 00:24:46,994
Ren Osugi.

232
00:24:48,237 --> 00:24:52,833
We have some sex scenes. Can you
handle that? -No problem.

233
00:24:53,437 --> 00:24:54,756
Are you psychic?

234
00:25:04,717 --> 00:25:05,706
Next.

235
00:25:05,917 --> 00:25:07,555
May I ask you a question?

236
00:25:08,237 --> 00:25:09,272
Can you smile?

237
00:25:10,557 --> 00:25:12,673
What kind of men
don't you like?

238
00:25:12,997 --> 00:25:15,431
Yoko Sugimura.
Nice to meet you.

239
00:25:16,957 --> 00:25:20,188
If I didn't have confidence
I wouldn't be an actress.

240
00:25:20,997 --> 00:25:22,146
Excuse me.

241
00:25:24,997 --> 00:25:30,025
When I was 2, mother decided
that I'd be an actress.

242
00:25:30,237 --> 00:25:32,831
Can you walk around the chair?

243
00:25:34,597 --> 00:25:35,871
Turn around.

244
00:25:36,077 --> 00:25:37,305
Next please.

245
00:25:43,837 --> 00:25:45,555
Nice meeting you.

246
00:25:49,157 --> 00:25:53,355
It's time for a break
from our schedule.

247
00:25:55,157 --> 00:25:58,706
We're 30 minutes late.
Let's take a 1 0 min. break.

248
00:25:58,917 --> 00:26:00,066
Sure.

249
00:26:06,717 --> 00:26:09,595
You don't seem too enthusiastic.

250
00:26:10,157 --> 00:26:13,149
Don't tell me you're
not interested anymore.

251
00:26:14,117 --> 00:26:15,869
It's not like that.

252
00:26:17,117 --> 00:26:18,470
Like what?

253
00:26:21,117 --> 00:26:24,587
I'm nervous myself.
I need to use the toilet.

254
00:26:47,357 --> 00:26:52,875
I lived in Paris for 3 years. And have
come back to Tokyo as a designer.

255
00:26:53,717 --> 00:26:55,673
I can't think about anything
else but being an actress.

256
00:26:55,877 --> 00:27:00,348
My office was only for adult videos.
-Keep her for another job.

257
00:27:00,557 --> 00:27:04,106
I'm not satisfied being
called a cover girl queen.

258
00:27:09,357 --> 00:27:12,588
This scar is from my 1st suicide
attempt and this is from the 2nd.

259
00:27:12,797 --> 00:27:15,834
I've been to an asylum 3 times.

260
00:27:16,757 --> 00:27:18,270
Next.

261
00:27:19,077 --> 00:27:21,671
Emi Kitani.
Pleased to meet you.

262
00:27:22,357 --> 00:27:24,791
We finished your
interview before.

263
00:27:25,077 --> 00:27:27,796
But I haven't finished
what I have to say.

264
00:27:28,237 --> 00:27:31,593
You have nice career, why
do you want to be an actress?

265
00:27:32,277 --> 00:27:37,226
I think I've been doing
very well, but...

266
00:27:38,357 --> 00:27:40,109
Sorry.

267
00:27:40,357 --> 00:27:43,986
I'm a children's nurse.
My work is very hard...

268
00:27:46,437 --> 00:27:47,916
Next please.

269
00:27:48,197 --> 00:27:50,313
Ms. Asami Yamasaki.

270
00:27:53,357 --> 00:27:54,676
Please.

271
00:28:08,157 --> 00:28:11,035
Asami Yamasaki.
-Have a seat

272
00:28:13,717 --> 00:28:16,311
Sorry for the delay.
-It's OK.

273
00:28:17,837 --> 00:28:21,307
Have you done any movies
or TV jobs?

274
00:28:22,037 --> 00:28:25,825
I've had many opportunities,
but actually haven't done any.

275
00:28:27,837 --> 00:28:31,546
Do you belong to any agency?
Not really.

276
00:28:31,757 --> 00:28:36,467
But I'm on keep
for a record Co. director.

277
00:28:36,837 --> 00:28:38,907
But we haven't contacted
each other recently.

278
00:28:39,117 --> 00:28:42,587
Which record company?
-Ace Records.

279
00:28:44,717 --> 00:28:47,356
Could you tell me your
personal contact's name?

280
00:28:48,757 --> 00:28:51,749
Japanese music dept.
Director Shibata.

281
00:28:58,277 --> 00:29:04,307
Since you quit your previous
job, you're unemployed?

282
00:29:04,677 --> 00:29:07,510
How do you manage your daily expenses?
lf you don't mind telling us.

283
00:29:08,157 --> 00:29:12,389
I help at a friend's shop. 3 times a week.
-What kind of shop?

284
00:29:13,237 --> 00:29:15,705
A small bar in Ginza.

285
00:29:16,037 --> 00:29:20,872
The owner used to be a class
mate in voice training.

286
00:29:21,757 --> 00:29:25,113
If I keep my costs low,
I have no money problems.

287
00:29:26,237 --> 00:29:28,307
Don't you want to lead
a luxurious life.

288
00:29:29,957 --> 00:29:32,312
Too poor isn't good.

289
00:29:32,677 --> 00:29:37,876
But I can afford books and CDs.
That's enough for me.

290
00:29:39,557 --> 00:29:41,593
Can I ask you about ballet?

291
00:29:42,917 --> 00:29:43,952
Certainly.

292
00:29:44,157 --> 00:29:47,115
You damaged your hips.
-That's correct.

293
00:29:47,277 --> 00:29:51,270
It must have been awful to
quit what you'd been doing.

294
00:29:52,917 --> 00:29:54,396
Yes.

295
00:29:55,517 --> 00:29:58,953
I must sound a bit rude but...

296
00:29:59,157 --> 00:30:03,833
Your writing says that quitting
what you liked...

297
00:30:04,037 --> 00:30:07,950
...is almost similar to accepting death.

298
00:30:08,917 --> 00:30:11,989
I was highly impressed.

299
00:30:13,757 --> 00:30:16,590
I think everybody has
similar experiences.

300
00:30:17,277 --> 00:30:21,509
In your lifetime when you have
something beyond your control.

301
00:30:22,037 --> 00:30:25,666
What can you do but accept it?

302
00:30:26,237 --> 00:30:28,956
I think that's life.

303
00:30:29,477 --> 00:30:30,830
I mean...

304
00:30:32,037 --> 00:30:36,235
I was amazed a young girl
like you understands that.

305
00:30:36,717 --> 00:30:42,030
I think you live your life
in a very thoughtful way.

306
00:30:42,277 --> 00:30:44,586
That's what I thought.

307
00:30:56,277 --> 00:30:58,108
Thank you very much.

308
00:31:05,397 --> 00:31:07,069
Are you finished?

309
00:31:10,357 --> 00:31:12,313
Thank you for coming.

310
00:31:12,477 --> 00:31:15,947
We may contact you later.
-Yes.

311
00:31:18,757 --> 00:31:20,748
Excuse me.

312
00:31:32,437 --> 00:31:35,668
May I call the next one?
-Let's have a 1 5 min break.

313
00:31:35,877 --> 00:31:36,912
Fine.

314
00:31:37,397 --> 00:31:40,594
Please tell Mr. Ito I'll be late.

315
00:31:48,957 --> 00:31:52,950
What do you think?
-She made me very nervous.

316
00:31:53,237 --> 00:31:55,592
I wanted a cigarette.

317
00:31:57,317 --> 00:32:00,150
You decided on her before
the audition.

318
00:32:00,757 --> 00:32:05,956
I like her much more than
her nice writing.

319
00:32:06,557 --> 00:32:10,106
I think you live your life
in a very thoughtful way.

320
00:32:10,277 --> 00:32:13,553
It's not an interviewer's
comment. I was stunned.

321
00:32:13,757 --> 00:32:17,670
Don't joke about that.
She really impressed me.

322
00:32:23,157 --> 00:32:26,832
I'm sure she's a serious
type of girl.

323
00:32:27,597 --> 00:32:32,512
She is better than her photo
and may also be good hearted.

324
00:32:35,077 --> 00:32:37,545
But I don't like her.

325
00:32:37,917 --> 00:32:40,556
What's wrong with her?

326
00:32:41,597 --> 00:32:43,235
Something chemical.

327
00:32:44,677 --> 00:32:48,875
Can't say exactly what's wrong.
I just don't like her.

328
00:33:09,557 --> 00:33:14,347
Misuzu?

329
00:33:14,557 --> 00:33:17,390
She looked nice, but...
-What?

330
00:33:18,197 --> 00:33:22,748
One of those girl things.
I don't understand girls. Do you?

331
00:33:26,837 --> 00:33:28,156
Thanks.

332
00:33:30,117 --> 00:33:35,874
Hey dad, about your remarriage. Preferably
someone who cooks better than Rie.

333
00:33:38,957 --> 00:33:40,788
Why are you in such a hurry?

334
00:33:41,077 --> 00:33:44,865
New discovery of another
dinosaur, from Argentina.

335
00:33:45,077 --> 00:33:48,353
That one could be older
than Euraptile. Really.

336
00:33:48,517 --> 00:33:50,906
I'll be busy collecting
information.

337
00:33:52,797 --> 00:33:54,549
Take a bath.

338
00:34:28,917 --> 00:34:30,635
Yes, hello.

339
00:34:31,397 --> 00:34:33,388
Sorry for calling so late.

340
00:34:33,557 --> 00:34:38,073
This is producer Aoyama.
I interviewed you today.

341
00:34:38,917 --> 00:34:42,751
Thank you for your time today.
-Not at all. Well...

342
00:34:45,797 --> 00:34:51,793
I wondered if you might have
some time to talk with me.

343
00:34:52,637 --> 00:34:55,390
Of course. I'd love to see you.

344
00:34:56,517 --> 00:35:01,716
When would suit you?
-Anytime would be fine, during the daytime.

345
00:35:02,037 --> 00:35:05,950
Really. Let me see.
For instance...

346
00:35:11,557 --> 00:35:12,910
Good night.

347
00:35:27,717 --> 00:35:29,389
This is the Aoyama residence.

348
00:35:29,797 --> 00:35:32,630
It's me.
-How is it?

349
00:35:33,197 --> 00:35:37,190
About Ms. Yamasaki.

350
00:35:37,837 --> 00:35:42,115
Without suspicion,
I called Ace Records.

351
00:35:44,197 --> 00:35:48,509
It's no big deal, but
something didn't seem right.

352
00:35:49,277 --> 00:35:50,710
What is it?

353
00:35:52,397 --> 00:35:55,946
Director Shibata isn't
at the company.

354
00:35:56,837 --> 00:36:00,113
To be precise,
he isn't there anymore.

355
00:36:03,037 --> 00:36:08,031
He's been missing for a year.

356
00:36:10,757 --> 00:36:12,793
He just disappeared.

357
00:36:18,437 --> 00:36:21,156
I'm nervous.

358
00:36:22,957 --> 00:36:27,747
Please relax, I won't ask
you any special questions.

359
00:36:29,877 --> 00:36:35,076
You only ask of me to enjoy
this nice food and talk?

360
00:36:35,597 --> 00:36:36,746
Absolutely.

361
00:36:37,197 --> 00:36:40,746
That's the best request
I've ever had.

362
00:36:42,877 --> 00:36:44,913
Just one question.

363
00:36:46,517 --> 00:36:49,429
Your director contact.

364
00:36:50,797 --> 00:36:52,867
Mr. Shibata?

365
00:36:54,077 --> 00:36:59,310
I'm sorry I said so at the
audition but...

366
00:36:59,957 --> 00:37:02,755
In fact I've never met him.

367
00:37:03,397 --> 00:37:07,629
I don't belong to
any actors agency.

368
00:37:08,077 --> 00:37:11,228
I was advised to answer you like that.

369
00:37:11,997 --> 00:37:14,192
Is that so?

370
00:37:15,957 --> 00:37:17,549
I didn't mean to tell a lie.

371
00:37:17,837 --> 00:37:22,706
It's OK. I've clarified that
question, that's no problem.

372
00:37:25,397 --> 00:37:26,910
Here we go.

373
00:37:28,717 --> 00:37:30,469
Looks wonderful.

374
00:37:35,757 --> 00:37:37,156
Go ahead.

375
00:37:49,877 --> 00:37:52,550
Yummy.
-Good.

376
00:37:58,397 --> 00:38:01,787
I hope I'm not asking you
too much but...

377
00:38:01,997 --> 00:38:04,431
If you have some free time,

378
00:38:05,357 --> 00:38:08,713
I'd like to talk to you more.

379
00:38:08,877 --> 00:38:13,792
I don't have anybody to be
frank with.

380
00:38:14,797 --> 00:38:20,030
If I'm good enough,
I'd love to.

381
00:38:20,557 --> 00:38:22,513
Really? I'm very happy
about that.

382
00:38:23,197 --> 00:38:26,826
I'll try not to bother you.

383
00:38:27,557 --> 00:38:33,746
I don't mind any place.

384
00:38:34,437 --> 00:38:36,507
Even on the telephone
would be fine.

385
00:38:37,437 --> 00:38:40,873
I'll write my mobile number
on my busniss card.

386
00:38:41,077 --> 00:38:43,307
Please call me anytime.

387
00:38:44,197 --> 00:38:48,076
Thank you very much.
Thank you for the meal too.

388
00:38:50,717 --> 00:38:52,912
I've decided.

389
00:38:53,917 --> 00:38:59,435
I don't care about the movie,
I'm interested only in her.

390
00:39:03,917 --> 00:39:08,069
Don't worry about the movie.
I'll handle that matter.

391
00:39:09,997 --> 00:39:12,511
But don't be too hasty.

392
00:39:13,437 --> 00:39:16,235
You wanted to have some time
to observe your prospect.

393
00:39:17,957 --> 00:39:21,711
Why are you so negative about
her? What's wrong with her?

394
00:39:21,877 --> 00:39:26,234
I only think that life
isn't so easy.

395
00:39:28,197 --> 00:39:31,712
She is beautiful, classy
and obedient.

396
00:39:32,637 --> 00:39:38,428
Such a woman not having any
boyfriends is unthinkable.

397
00:39:40,197 --> 00:39:43,826
I checked out her associates,
none are accessible.

398
00:39:45,397 --> 00:39:48,434
The bar she was talking about
is also an unknown.

399
00:39:49,957 --> 00:39:54,235
We can't reach anybody
who knows her.

400
00:39:54,477 --> 00:39:58,709
I wasn't born yesterday.
I won't be fooled this easily.

401
00:39:59,037 --> 00:40:02,029
I trust myself over some
others evaluation.

402
00:40:02,597 --> 00:40:06,510
If there's any trouble, I
can solve it.

403
00:40:07,877 --> 00:40:09,026
OK.

404
00:40:09,477 --> 00:40:13,868
You said I could find my
ideal woman from an audition.

405
00:40:15,197 --> 00:40:17,506
I appreciate it.

406
00:40:22,477 --> 00:40:23,512
Hey Aoyama.

407
00:40:24,477 --> 00:40:28,152
Promise me one thing.
Don't call her.

408
00:40:29,197 --> 00:40:31,631
Hopefully it's my miscalculation.

409
00:40:32,237 --> 00:40:34,592
It's going to effect your
whole life.

410
00:40:34,797 --> 00:40:36,753
Don't be so hasty.

411
00:40:41,917 --> 00:40:43,635
Cool down a bit.

412
00:40:49,037 --> 00:40:51,551
Alright. I promise you.

413
00:41:58,197 --> 00:41:59,994
You're not sick are you?

414
00:42:01,197 --> 00:42:04,030
It is rare for you to
take a day off.

415
00:42:04,517 --> 00:42:07,714
Since I've worked for you,
I've never seen you like this.

416
00:42:08,637 --> 00:42:09,752
Oh well...

417
00:42:10,397 --> 00:42:15,425
It's good to have a break.
You might be a little tired.

418
00:42:15,797 --> 00:42:20,473
Since your wife died, you've
worked very hard for your son.

419
00:42:20,717 --> 00:42:26,075
Forming your own company which is
doing quite well. You work too much.

420
00:42:27,837 --> 00:42:33,469
I wish my husband was like you.
My life would be easier.

421
00:42:37,597 --> 00:42:39,872
You must have a nice
girlfriend.

422
00:42:59,157 --> 00:43:01,273
I'm sure you do.

423
00:43:01,757 --> 00:43:06,273
Men can't maintain without
female support.

424
00:43:44,637 --> 00:43:47,993
I've finished.
I'm going home.

425
00:43:48,197 --> 00:43:51,394
Bye.
-See You tomorrow.

426
00:44:09,157 --> 00:44:10,715
I'm leaving.

427
00:44:12,197 --> 00:44:13,915
See you.

428
00:44:21,397 --> 00:44:23,388
Do you have something
to tell me?

429
00:44:24,197 --> 00:44:27,109
Not really.
See you tomorrow.

430
00:44:28,277 --> 00:44:29,756
Bye.

431
00:46:19,357 --> 00:46:21,154
Hello... This is Aoyama.

432
00:46:21,357 --> 00:46:22,506
Really? Good.

433
00:46:23,157 --> 00:46:27,309
I thought you wouldn't
phone me anymore.

